      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly lately i just feel like such a weight on everyone. my daughter is always running around trying to help me with things i used to do myself... i can see how tired she gets just looking at me. it feels like everything i do now is just more work for them. i dont want to be a nuisance anymore.",
